{"tid":1925282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[澄清]意大利只喺\"購買\"向中國呼吸機同口罩，而非中國向意大利\"捐贈\"","createTime":"2020-03-14T09:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T22:48:25.000Z","uid":78519,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f45adae1d6f8599f0e1336c23a6b7ea6828b8ffe","tid":1925282,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"[澄清]意大利只喺&rdquo; 購買&rdquo;向中國呼吸機同口罩，而非中國向意大利捐贈<br />\n<br />\n3月10日，羅馬-週二，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>外長迪馬約（Luigi Di Maio）和中國外長王毅通電後，雙方將簽訂合同，將有超過200萬個口罩(唔喺N95，喺普通外科口罩)和約1萬個呼吸機(pulmonary ventilators)從中國運抵意大利。</strong></span></strong><br />\n     王毅向迪馬約保證，在其他歐洲國家提出類似要求後，意大利向中國公司採購呼吸機訂單會優先於其他歐洲國家。<br />\n     王毅還告訴迪馬約，中國政府已指示其公司出口200萬個醫用口罩。<br />\n     首先，中國準備發送10萬套高科技口罩(high-tech masks)和20,000套防護服，以及50萬套擦拭採集棉棒(swabs)。<br />\nSource: 安莎通訊社，是意大利最大的通訊社<a href=\"https://www.ansa.it/english/news/2020/03/10/2-mn-masks-1000-ventilators-coming-from-china-5_be78418e-ee39-4c2f-8012-5203372d3a46.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ansa.it%2Fenglish%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F10%2F2-mn-masks-1000-ventilators-coming-from-china-5_be78418e-ee39-4c2f-8012-5203372d3a46.html&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=d871ba91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ansa.it/english/news/2020/03/10/2-mn-masks-1000-ventilators-coming-from-china-5_be78418e-ee39-4c2f-8012-5203372d3a46.html</a>"},{"pid":"a44fd0574f97d0fe12a4bfcf36f5664387d5f262","tid":1925282,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dd2c516fffd018f901257e728b942921145c69","tid":1925282,"uid":199893,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而中方係迫使日本捐款口罩"},{"pid":"227d0ddb91d0b67ed6249d8295824fe04e6f3e97","tid":1925282,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"係, 我留意到新聞都係話運抵, 無話捐, 引人誤以為捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da2ae0bf847ce10e35208939015a54fd841ffd9","tid":1925282,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"Reddit有意大利人話唔好信支那宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1924067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1924067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c704dcedba96b3dd3277959d6ffe5f00192b3f6","tid":1925282,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"Reddit有個post話支那送大禮 意大利人回覆話我有俾錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1924988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1924988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39827d1fad2cb4e980d60a167e9ade95e550f433","tid":1925282,"uid":71071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"以後用口罩嚟做貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723710041cbee9eb6d7c7796a0a892d378af1071","tid":1925282,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係之前外國捐俾中國?"},{"pid":"062dfd8bddf0094342f62b82a01885237b9f1c17","tid":1925282,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"中國準備發送10萬套<span style=\"color: red;\">高科技口罩</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\